§0
§0Welcome to the third§0
§0Government Gazette,§0
§0for the week ending§0
§02019-07-21, with me,§0
§0your Mayor, AllenY.
#- §lCitizenship§0
§0
§0With the passage of§0
§0a citizenship reform§0
§0bill, there is a new§0
§0thread and process§0
§0for gaining citizen-§0
§0ship. Feel free to§0
§0use the suggested§0
§0form to organise§0
§0your response. This§0
§0should be the last
#- major change to the§0
§0process for quite a§0
§0while, and appli-§0
§0cations are en-§0
§0couraged.
#- §lJudge election§0
§0
§0DCHERO has been§0
§0elected as Judge in§0
§0the byelection for§0
§0my former position,§0
§0with a large majority.§0
§0His term is not a§0
§0full one, and lasts§0
§0only until August.§0
§0Congratulations to§0
§0him, and best of luck.
#- §lJudicial review§0
§0§land limitation of§0
§0§lactions reform§0
§0
§0Continuing with my§0
§0legal reform agenda§0
§0as Mayor, I have put§0
§0up for discussion§0
§0the second major§0
§0bill discussion thread§0
§0of my Mayordom. It§0
§0seeks to introduce
#- judicial review, and§0
§0limit actions being§0
§0brought after a cer-§0
§0tain amount of time.
#- §lWest Canal re-§0
§0§lstored§0
§0
§0West Canal has been§0
§0restored from its§0
§0period of function§0
§0as defensive infra-§0
§0structure to a func-§0
§0tional canal, exactly§0
§0as it was before.
#- §lMargaritaville§0
§0§lopen§0
§0
§0Previously Pinkerton,§0
§0the underutilised§0
§0land in the southwest§0
§0of the city is now§0
§0open for settlement,§0
§0thanks to the Cup§0
§0for Infrastructure.
#- §lQuotations for§0
§0§lMount Augusta§0
§0
§0I have published a§0
§0short compilation of§0
§0quotes which reflect,§0
§0to some extent, my§0
§0views on the gover-§0
§0nance of Mount Au-§0
§0gusta. I publicise it§0
§0as it is a document of§0
§0governance, of sorts.
